1. Masuk ke Mode Konfigurasi
abiyasa#configure terminal
Enter configuration commands, one per line.  End with CNTL/Z.
abiyasa(config)#

2. Masukkan Konfigurasi IKEv2 (Phase 1)
ip local pool VPN-POOL 192.168.80.1 192.168.80.50

crypto ikev2 proposal FORTI-PROP 
 encryption aes-cbc-256
 integrity sha256
 group 14
exit

crypto ikev2 policy FORTI-POL
 proposal FORTI-PROP
exit

crypto ikev2 keyring FORTI-KEY
 peer ANY
  address 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0
  pre-shared-key KunciRahasiaVPN
exit


Karena Anda sudah memasukkan ketiganya, statusnya sekarang sudah valid.

Sekarang, Anda berada di dalam abiyasa(config-ikev2-keyring)#. Mari kita lanjutkan ke tahap berikutnya untuk membuat Authorization Policy dan Profile.

Silakan masukkan baris perintah berikut:
4. Lanjutkan ke Authorization Policy & Profile
exit
!
crypto ikev2 authorization policy FORTI-AUTHOR
 pool VPN-POOL
 dns 8.8.8.8
exit
!
crypto ikev2 profile FORTI-PROFILE
 match identity remote address 0.0.0.0
 identity local address 192.168.30.100
 authentication remote pre-share
 authentication local pre-share
 keyring FORTI-KEY
 aaa authorization group local list default FORTI-AUTHOR
 virtual-template 1
exit

